data.description: A rare opportunity in desirable Hampton Creek! This is the one you’ve been waiting for and it’s ready for you!  Lovely 4/3.5/3 home with plenty of room for gracious living.  Tile flooring in downstairs living and wet areas. Wood flooring in spacious primary bedroom with walk-in closet and seating nook. 2” plantation blinds throughout, huge back yard, screened covered patio with gas tap for easy addition of summer kitchen or gas grill.  Granite countertops in kitchen, stainless steel appliances, programmable faucet and refrigerator included.  Extra space on stair landing for reading chair and lamp and to easily keep game room area in view.  Enjoy movies in the privacy of your home in the media room. Conveniently located with easy access to The Woodlands, Grand Parkway, I-45 and the ExxonMobil campus. Don’t miss this one!
